                        <summary/>
                        <msItem xml:id="ms_i1">
                            <title type="complete" ref="LIT7368demons"/>
                            <note>On the upper part of the scroll, on the left column, below the upper picture.</note>
                            <incipit xml:lang="gez">በስመ፡ <gap reason="omitted"/> ጸሎት፡ በእንተ፡ <surplus>ወ</surplus>ባርያ፡ ወጋኔን፡ <sic>ወጽልዋጊ፡</sic>
                                ወማርተኛ<supplied reason="omitted">፡</supplied> ወተ<supplied reason="omitted">ን</supplied>ኵለኛ፡
                                <gap reason="omitted"/> ታዖስ፡ አዜ፡ አዝያስ፡ <gap reason="omitted"/> በኃይለ፡ ዝንቱ፡ አንብቦ፡ ወአስተናግሮ፡ ለቡዳ፡ መሠርይ፡ ወለሌጌዎን፡
                                ኢኩይ፡ ለቍርፀት፡ ወለፍልፀት፡ ለዓይነት፡ ወለውግዓት፡ ለዛር፡ ወለንዳድ፡ ለቡዳ፡ ወለበዓለ፡ ግብር፡ ወለትግርትያ፡ ወሾቶላይ፡ ጋኔን፡ ወውርዝልያ፡ ወደባስ፡ ወአሶ፡ 
                                ወነቀጥቃጥ፡ ወቅርጥማት፡ ወአጽረ፡ ሽንት፡ ወአልጉም፡ ወጽልዋጊ፡ ወማርተኛ፡ ወተንኵነኛ፡ ወእከያኛ፡ ወስራይ፡ ወኵሉ፡ ደዌ፡ ሥጋ፡ ወነፍስ፡</incipit>
                            <textLang mainLang="gez"/>
                        </msItem>
                        <msItem xml:id="ms_i2">
                            <title type="complete" ref="LIT7374Zar"/>
                            <note>On the upper part of the scroll, on the left column, below the upper picture.</note>
                            <incipit xml:lang="gez">በስመ፡ <gap reason="omitted"/> ጸሎተ፡ ዛር፡ ቄቄል፡ ቤቴል፡ ሮቤል፡</incipit>
                            <textLang mainLang="gez"/>
                        </msItem>
                        <msItem xml:id="ms_i3">
                            <title type="complete" ref="LIT4506Salam"/>
                            <note>On the upper part of the scroll, on the left column, below the upper picture.</note>
                            <incipit xml:lang="gez">ሰላም፡ ለገጽኪ፡ ዘጥቀ፡ ይልሂ፡ እምስነ፡ ከዋክብት፡ ወርህ፡ ወእምስነ፡ ፀሐይ፡ መብርሂ፡ <gap reason="omitted"/> ኦእግዝዕትየ፡
                                ማርያም፡ <sic>አድኅንኒ፡</sic> እመክራ፡ ሥጋ፡ ወነፍስ፡</incipit>
                            <textLang mainLang="gez"/>
                        </msItem>
                        <msItem xml:id="ms_i4">
                            <title type="complete" ref="LIT6786MatthewEight"/>
                            <note>Account of the healing by Jesus of the two possessed by demons in Mt. 8:28-34. Written on the upper part of the 
                                scroll, on the middle column, below the upper picture.</note>
                            <textLang mainLang="gez"/>
                        </msItem>
                        <msItem xml:id="ms_i5">
                            <title type="complete" ref="LIT7365PrayerJesus"/>
                            <note>On the upper part of the scroll, on the right column, below the upper picture.</note>
                            <incipit xml:lang="gez">በስመ፡ <gap reason="omitted"/> ይትነሣዕ፡ እግዚአብሔር፡ ወይዘረው፡ ፀሩ፡ ወይጕየዩ፡ ፀላዕቱ፡ እምቅድመ፡
                                ገፁ፡ ሐተወ፡ አፍአተ፡ አንሣእኩ፡ አዕይንትየ፡ መንገለ፡ አድባር፡ እምአይቴ፡ ይምፃዕ፡ ረዲዖትየ፡ <gap reason="omitted"/> ኦአምላከ፡ ዳዊት፡ አድኅኖ፡
                                እምዕለት፡ ዕኪት፡ ወእምሠአታተ፡ <gap reason="omitted"/> ንዒ፡ ማርያም፡ ለዕውር፡ ብርሃኑ፡ ወንኢ፡ ድንግል፡ <surplus>ድንግል፡</surplus>
                                ለጽሙዕ፡ ዓንቅዕተ፡ ወይኑ፡</incipit>
                            <textLang mainLang="gez"/>
                        </msItem>
                        <msItem xml:id="ms_i6">
                            <title type="complete" ref="LIT7042PrayerMichael"/>
                            <note>On the middle part of the scroll, on the left column, below the second picture.</note>
                            <incipit xml:lang="gez">በእንተ፡ <sic>ለ</sic>ጌዎን፡ ርኩስ፡ ዘይሰልብ፡ ልበ፡ ሰብእ፡ ወይመጽእ፡ ከመ፡ ጽላሎት፡ <gap reason="omitted"/>
                                አምሐልኵከ፡ ወአወገዝኩከ፡ በ፫አካላት፡ ወበ፩መለኮት፡ ወበ፭ቅንዋተ፡ መስቀሉ፡ ለእግዚእነ፡ ኢየሱስ፡ ክርስቶስ፡ <gap reason="omitted"/> ለሥሃ፡ ኅምዙ፡ 
                                ለሞት፡ ወተቀጥጠ፡ ኃይሉ፡ ለሰይጣን፡ ቍርፀት፡ ወፍልጸት፡ ዓይነት፡ ውግዓት፡ ዛር፡ ወንዳድ፡ ቡዳ፡ ወበዓለ፡ ግብር፡ ወትግርትያ፡ አድኅኖ፡ ለገብርከ፡</incipit>
                            <textLang mainLang="gez"/>
                        </msItem>
                        <msItem xml:id="ms_i7">
                            <title type="complete" ref="LIT7345SeddatSayt"/>
                            <note>On the middle part of the scroll, on the left column, below the second picture.</note>
                            <incipit xml:lang="gez">በስመ፡ <gap reason="omitted"/> ጸሎት፡ በእንተ፡ ስደቶሙ፡ ለሰይጣናት፡ ዝጋኔን፡ ይትሐረድ፡ ጶጶለጽኝ፡ ጨለጓፍ፡ 
                                <gap reason="omitted"/> ውጉዛነ፡ ይኩኑ፡ አጋንንት፡ ፀዋጋን፡ ወሰብዕ፡ መሠርያን<supplied reason="omitted">፡</supplied> 
                                ወእምውግዓት፡ ሣቅሣቂያን፡ ወእምትግርቲያ፡ እቡያን፡ ወእምቡዳ፡ ቀታልያን፡</incipit>
                            <textLang mainLang="gez"/>
                        </msItem>
                        <msItem xml:id="ms_i8">
                            <title type="complete" ref="LIT4007Salotb"/>
                            <note>On the middle part of the scroll, on the right column, below the second picture.</note>
                            <incipit xml:lang="gez">በስመ፡ <gap reason="omitted"/> ጸሎት፡ በእንተ፡ መፍትሔ፡ ስራይ፡ ዘተቀድሐ፡ እም፹ወ፩መፃሕፍት፡ ዘወጽአት፡ 
                                እምኢየሩሳሌም፡ ዘሞዖሙ፡ ለመሰርያን፡ ወለደጋምያነ፡ አስማት፡ ወለመታርያነ፡ ዕፅ፡ እስላም፡ ወክርስቲያን፡ ጋላ፡ ወሽንቅላ፡ <gap reason="omitted"/>
                                ፍታሕ፡ ክሙናዝር፡ ኤልናዝር፡ <gap reason="omitted"/> ፍታሕ፡ ዘተገብረ፡ ወዘተደግመ፡ በነምር፡ ወበዝዕብ፡ ወበአንበሳ፡ ጋማ፡ ደጊሞሙ፡ ወበዘሆን፡ ሐሞት፡ 
                                ወበዘልበደ<supplied reason="omitted">፡</supplied> ሥጋ፡</incipit>
                            <textLang mainLang="gez"/>
                        </msItem>
                        <msItem xml:id="ms_i9">
                            <title type="complete" ref="LIT7344FethatSer"/>
                            <note>On the lower part of the scroll, on the left column, below the third picture. Prayer with a reference to 
                                Metropolitan <persName ref="PRS8388SalamaI"/>, who died in <date when="1867">1867</date>.</note>
                            <incipit xml:lang="gez">በስመ፡ <gap reason="omitted"/> ጸሎተ፡ ፍትሐተ፡ ስራይ፡ ኤፍዛዜዎስ፡ ኤፍዛዜዎስ፡ ኤፍዛዜዎስ፡ መርታዳ፡ መርታዳ፡
                                መርታዳ፡ አክሎክ፡ አክሎክ፡ አክሎክ፡ ፍታሕ፡ ዳዊ፡ ፍታሕ፡ ጉሐኤል፡ ፍታሕ፡ ቀንተው፡ ፍታሕ፡ ቀርነለው፡ ዘፈታሕኮሙ፡ ለጴጥሮስ፡ ወለጳውሎሥ፡ እምዋቅሕተ፡
                                ብርት፡ አነኒ፡ ፈታሕኩ፡ ለንጉሥነ፡ መፍቀሬ፡ አምላክ፡ በጳጳስነ፡ <persName ref="PRS8388SalamaI">አቡነ፡ ሰላማ፡</persName> ይትፈታሕ፡ 
                                ዝሥራይ፡ በላእለ፡ ገብርከ፡</incipit>
                            <textLang mainLang="gez"/>
                        </msItem>
                        <msItem xml:id="ms_i10">
                            <title type="complete" ref="LIT7364migraine"/>
                            <note>On the lower part of the scroll, on the middle column, below the third picture.</note>
                            <incipit xml:lang="gez">በስመ፡ <gap reason="omitted"/> ጸሎት፡ በእንተ፡ ፈልጸተ፡ ርዕስ፡ አክራድዮስ፡ አውግንዩስ፡ አውግንዩስ፡</incipit>
                            <textLang mainLang="gez"/>
                        </msItem>
                        <msItem xml:id="ms_i11">
                            <title type="complete" ref="LIT7343QwersatAna"/>
                            <note>On the lower part of the scroll, on the middle column, below the third picture.</note>
                            <incipit xml:lang="gez">በስመ፡ <gap reason="omitted"/> ጸሎት፡ በእንተ፡ ቍርፀት፡ ወከብድ፡ አምላከ፡ አናንያ፡ ወሚሣኤል፡ ዘአድኃንኮሙ፡ 
                                እምእቶነ፡ እሳት፡ ዘይነድድ፡ በሂሩትከ፡</incipit>
                            <textLang mainLang="gez"/>
                        </msItem>
                        <msItem xml:id="ms_i12">
                            <title type="complete" ref="LIT4624Prayer"/>
                            <note>On the lower part of the scroll, on the middle column, below the third picture.</note>
                            <incipit xml:lang="gez">በስመ፡ <gap reason="omitted"/> ጸሎት፡ በእንተ፡ ውግዓት፡ ምድምያስ፡ ምድምያስ፡ ምድምያስ፡</incipit>
                            <textLang mainLang="gez"/>
                        </msItem>
                        <msItem xml:id="ms_i13">
                            <title type="complete" ref="LIT7342Nedad"/>
                            <note>On the lower part of the scroll, on the middle column, below the third picture.</note>
                            <incipit xml:lang="gez">ጸሎተ፡ ንዳድ፡ ሰንደ፡ ለፎን፡</incipit>
                            <textLang mainLang="gez"/>
                        </msItem>
                        <msItem xml:id="ms_i14">
                            <title type="complete" ref="LIT4577MagicPr"/>
                            <note>On the lower part of the scroll, on the right column, below the third picture.</note>
                            <incipit xml:lang="gez">ጸሎት፡ ቅርጥማት፡ ሸምዳን፡ ሸምዳን፡ ሸምዳን፡ ሸርታን፡ ሸርታን፡ ሸርታን፡</incipit>
                            <textLang mainLang="gez"/>
                        </msItem>
                        <msItem xml:id="ms_i15">
                            <title type="complete" ref="LIT7341AynatQabu"/>
                            <note>On the lower part of the scroll, on the right column, below the third picture.</note>
                            <incipit xml:lang="gez">ጸሎተ፡ ዓይነት፡ ቀበሹን፡ ቀበሹን፡ ቀበሹን፡ ሐረፃን፡ ሐረፃን፡ ሐረፃን፡</incipit>
                            <textLang mainLang="gez"/>
                        </msItem>
                        <msItem xml:id="ms_i16">
                            <title type="complete" ref="LIT5196MagicPrayer"/>
                            <note>On the lower part of the scroll, on the right column, below the third picture.</note>
                            <incipit xml:lang="gez">ጸሎት፡ በእንተ፡ ግርማ፡ ወሞገሥ፡ ግርማ፡ ግርማ፡ ግርማ፡ አሸ፡ መሸ፡</incipit>
                            <textLang mainLang="gez"/>
                        </msItem>
