                        <decoDesc>
                            <decoNote xml:id="d1" type="miniature">
                                <desc><term key="MagicDrawing">Coloured magic picture</term> without title.</desc>
                            </decoNote>
                            <decoNote xml:id="d2" type="miniature">
                                <desc>Coloured picture representing <persName ref="PRS2548Basilide"/> spearing Satan (indicated with 
                                    <foreign xml:lang="gez">ቅዱስ፡ ፋሲለደስ፡ ዘከመ፡ ረገዞ፡ ለሰይጣን፡</foreign>) and <persName ref="PRS8065Raguel"/> 
                                    spearing the Dragon (indicated with <foreign xml:lang="gez">ቅዱስ፡ ራጉኤል፡ ዘከመ፡ ረገዞ፡ ለከይሲ፡</foreign>). Near the 
                                    Dragon, Satan is depicted holding the souls of the damned (indicated with <foreign xml:lang="gez">ነፍሳት፡</foreign>),
                                    below <persName ref="PRS8065Raguel"/> and a lion indicated with <foreign xml:lang="gez">አንበሳ፡</foreign>.</desc>
                            </decoNote>
                            <decoNote xml:id="d3" type="miniature">
                                <desc>Coloured picture representing the <term key="TrueCross">Cross</term> indicated with 
                                    <foreign xml:lang="gez">መስቀለ፡ ኢየሱስ፡</foreign>, <term key="demon">Satan</term> indicated with 
                                    <foreign xml:lang="gez">ሰይጣን፡ ጽዋሪ፡</foreign>, the Virgin Mary indicated with 
                                    <foreign xml:lang="gez">ጽዮን፡</foreign>, a tabot indicated with <foreign xml:lang="gez">ታቦት፡</foreign>, 
